  "detailed_description": "<strong>HOMETOWN WAR History</strong><br>The Battle for Sihang Warehouse took place from October 26 to November 1, 1937<br>The Battle for Sihang Warehouse held out against numerous waves of Imperial Japanese Army and covered National Revolutionary Army retreating west during the Battle of Shanghai. <br><br><br><br><strong>HOMETOWN WAR</strong><br>Multiplayer FPS Game<br><br>This include 5 Game Modes:<br><br>Team Deathmatch<br>Team Deathmatch Stage<br>Deathmatch<br>Conquest <br>Rush<br><br><br>SinglePlayer mode : Players and our AI fight against enemy AI<br><br>Multiplayer mode : Support to 8 players <br><br>The LOBBY ( Listen Server )<br><br>Weapon Guns : WWII weapons that existed before 1937<br><br>Map : <br>Battle of Shanghai ( The Battle zone of Bazi Bridge ) ( V0.2.01 )<br>The Battle for Sihang Warehouse<br>Battle Zone ( simulation )",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>HOMETOWN WAR History</strong><br>The Battle for Sihang Warehouse took place from October 26 to November 1, 1937<br>The Battle for Sihang Warehouse held out against numerous waves of Imperial Japanese Army and covered National Revolutionary Army retreating west during the Battle of Shanghai. <br><br><br><br><strong>HOMETOWN WAR</strong><br>Multiplayer FPS Game<br><br>This include 5 Game Modes:<br><br>Team Deathmatch<br>Team Deathmatch Stage<br>Deathmatch<br>Conquest <br>Rush<br><br><br>SinglePlayer mode : Players and our AI fight against enemy AI<br><br>Multiplayer mode : Support to 8 players <br><br>The LOBBY ( Listen Server )<br><br>Weapon Guns : WWII weapons that existed before 1937<br><br>Map : <br>Battle of Shanghai ( The Battle zone of Bazi Bridge ) ( V0.2.01 )<br>The Battle for Sihang Warehouse<br>Battle Zone ( simulation )",
